OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWidely
OL,6,Fstaying hot into the evening, however
OL,7,Fa swathe of showery rain and
OL,8,Fthunderstorms may fringe the east
OL,9,Fduring the early hours. Drier and
OL,10,Fclearer further west, with another
OL,11,Fvery warm night expected generally,
OL,12,Fslightly less so than Thursday night.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FEarly showery rain and
OL,15,Fthunderstorms soon clearing eastwards.
OL,16,FBecoming fine with further sunshine
OL,17,Ffor a time, still hot, but markedly
OL,18,Fless so than Friday. Further showers
OL,19,Fand thunderstorms possible later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
