OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWhile
OL,6,Fstill warm, fresher conditions
OL,7,Fspreading eastwards Sunday, with more
OL,8,Fseasonable temperatures then expected.
OL,9,FSunday seeing sunshine and showers.
OL,10,FMainly fine Monday, with Tuesday then
OL,11,Fperhaps more unsettled.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
